==English==
===Noun===
'''slag'''
#The [[impurity|impurities]] which result and are separated out when [[melt]]ing a [[metal]] or [[refine|refining]] it from its [[ore]]; also, [[vitrify|vitrified]] cinders
#The [[scoria]] of a [[volcano]]
#(''UK & Australia'') {{pejorative}} a [[woman]] (sometimes a [[man]]) who has [[loose]] [[morals]] relating to [[sex]].

[[category:Australian English]]
[[category:UK]]

====Synonyms====
* (''impurities from a metal'') [[dross]], [[recrement]]
* (''loose woman'') see [[WikiSaurus:promiscuous woman]]

===Transitive Verb===
'''to slag'''
# to make slag
# to talk badly about someone; to denigrate someone

===Related / Derived Terms===
#slag off - talk [[insult|insultingly]] to or about someone

